thread.title: BRIEF-Shanghai Kindly Enterprise Development Group units to set up unit and JV

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shanghai Kindly Enterprise Development Group units to set up unit and JV

organizations.name: shanghai kindly enterprise development group co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Shanghai Kindly Enterprise Development Group Co Ltd
* Says co’s Zhuhai-based wholly owned unit plans to invest 30 million yuan to set up a Guangdong-based wholly owned medical supply chain management unit
* Says co’s Shanghai-based unit plans to invest 17 million yuan to set up a Shanghai-based medical instrument JV with partner and unit will hold 85 percent stake in the JV
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/6eEPxn ; goo.gl/T5NFiC
